arts.ttl: Rosenior's Strasbourg moves into contention for Champions League spot
arts.sum: Liam Rosenior’s Strasbourg firmly moved into contention for Champions League qualification after winning 1-0 at struggling Reims on Sunday. Strasbourg was level on 49 points with third-placed Marseille, which was looking to snap a three-game losing streak when it hosted Toulouse later Sunday.
